# Smart File Organizer

**Smart File Organizer** is a lightweight desktop application that automatically organizes messy folders into structured categories such as **Images, Videos, Documents, Archives, and more**.

The application is designed to help users quickly clean up disorganized directories with a **simple one-click interface**.

Developed using **Python and PySide6**, the software provides a fast and user-friendly way to manage files efficiently.

---

## Features

• Automatically organizes files into categorized folders
• Simple and intuitive graphical interface
• Splash screen support for better user experience
• Lightweight and fast performance
• One-click folder organization
• Desktop installer for easy installation

---

## Versions

This repository contains **two versions of the application**.

### Free Version

The free version includes the core functionality of the software.

Features:

• Organize files into categories automatically
• Select folder and organize files with one click
• Clean and simple GUI
• Windows installer available

This version will remain **free and stable without further updates**.

---

### Pro Version

The **Pro Version** includes advanced features and cross-platform builds.

Features:

• License key activation system
• Improved file organization features
• Windows installer
• macOS build support
• Automated build and release using GitHub Actions

The Pro version is automatically built and released using a **CI/CD pipeline**.

---

