---

## Installation

### Windows

1. Download the latest installer from the **Releases** section.
2. Run the installer.
3. Launch **Smart File Organizer** from the Start Menu or Desktop.

---

## How It Works

1. Open the application.
2. Select the folder you want to organize.
3. Click **Organize Files**.
4. The application automatically categorizes files into appropriate folders.

Example categories:

• Images
• Videos
• Documents
• Archives
• Others

---

## Technologies Used

Python
PySide6 (Qt for Python)
PyInstaller
Inno Setup Compiler
GitHub Actions (CI/CD)

---

## Automated Build Pipeline

The Pro version uses **GitHub Actions** to automate the build and release process.

Pipeline steps include:

• Installing dependencies
• Building executable using PyInstaller
• Creating Windows installer using Inno Setup
• Building macOS version
• Publishing release automatically to GitHub

